Date: 2026-02-09
Recipe: Cara Cara Orange

Ingredients:
  130g sucrose
  18g skim_milk_powder
  1g avacream
  45g corn_syrup_42
  280g whole_milk
  280g heavy_cream
  120g orange_juice
  10g orange_peel
  1g salt

Process Notes:
  Based on Salt & Straw Lemon recipe with cara cara oranges.
  Used avacream instead of xanthan.
  Added juice, zest, and salt after pasteurization and cooling.
  Churned to -4°C in 12 minutes.

Tasting Notes:
  Came out great!
